<h2>Carp Fishery – Erliefnis Baggerweier Remerschen</h2>
<p><em>A unique place between nature, fishing and social moments</em></p>
<p>In the heart of the natural site Erliefnis Baggerweier in Remerschen, the carp fishery invites visitors to experience a unique combination of nature, relaxation and fishing passion. Located in a green environment close to the Moselle river, this site has become over the years a true leisure destination where anglers, families, friends and companies gather for authentic outdoor moments.</p>
<h3>An exceptional natural setting</h3>
<p>Surrounded by peaceful landscapes and preserved nature, the carp fishery offers an ideal place to relax away from daily stress. The two dedicated carp fishing ponds blend perfectly into the environment and create a calm and relaxing atmosphere.</p>
<p>The site offers more than thirty comfortable fishing platforms, some of which are accessible for people with reduced mobility.</p>
<h3>Fishing for everyone</h3>
<p>At the carp fishery, fishing is an accessible leisure activity for everyone. Whether experienced angler, beginner or curious visitor, everything is designed so everyone can enjoy the experience.</p>
<p>Accessibility is a priority, ensuring easy and comfortable access for all visitors, including people with reduced mobility.</p>
<h3>Responsible fishing</h3>
<p>Fishing is practiced under a strict “No Kill” principle, protecting fish and preserving the ecosystem. Carp are released after being caught.</p>
<h3>Competitions and events</h3>
<p>The carp fishery is also a meeting point for the fishing community, with regular competitions bringing together participants from the region.</p>
<h3>Equipment rental</h3>
<p>Fishing equipment can be rented on site, allowing beginners and visitors without gear to enjoy the experience.</p>
<h3>Tailor-made events</h3>
<p>The site is suitable for private and professional events such as birthdays, company outings, team building or association gatherings.</p>
<p>Each event can be customized to create a unique experience.</p>
<h3>A place of relaxation and sharing</h3>
<p>The carp fishery is not only about fishing but also about sharing time in a natural and relaxing environment by the water.</p>
<p>Whether for a few hours or a full day, it offers an authentic outdoor experience in Remerschen.</p>